column1: Night of the Living Dead Amateur (morning meet) results

Create: 10/22/2011 - 13:05 Author: Staff Below are the results for the Night of the Living Dead Amateur session. Elisa Bird (98.4) was the winner on the women's division with a best deadlift of 214.9lbs. Steve Flaming (264) was the winner in the Men's division with a winning deadlift of 760.5lbs
